    "However, in the cases of multimodal data from sources like LiDAR, RGB-D camera or Radar, voxelization can lead to information loss and increased computational complexity, especially in complex scenes.",
    "Therefore, the development of attention models that focus on efficient feature extraction and fusion would be highly beneficial.",
    "• As point clouds continue to grow in size with the advancement of 3D technologies, the need for larger storage space becomes increasingly critical.",
    "Hence, a future direction should focus on the development of updated mechanisms that efficiently support the handling of 3D point cloud big data.",
    "• The utilization of cloud capabilities for point cloud processing is essential to consider."
